<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Drittanbieter-Lizenzen · budget-app</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 20px 80px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: #1c1c1f;
      background: #fafafa;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body { color: #e6e6e8; background: #15151a; }
      h2 { border-color: #2a2a32; }
      details, .summary-card { background: #1d1d23; border-color: #2a2a32; }
      summary { color: #d6d6dc; }
      .meta { color: #9a9aa3; }
      pre { background: #0e0e12; border-color: #2a2a32; }
      a { color: #6ab8ff; }
      .pill { background: #2a2a32; color: #d6d6dc; }
    }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 4px; }
    .lead { color: #6a6a73; margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 13px; }
    h2 {
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: #6a6a73;
      margin: 32px 0 12px;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e3e8;
    }
    .summary-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e3e3e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .summary-card ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      columns: 2;
      column-gap: 32px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .summary-card li { margin: 2px 0; break-inside: avoid; }
    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #eef0f3;
      color: #1c1c1f;
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-left: 6px;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    details {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e3e3e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: #1c1c1f;
    }
    .meta {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6a6a73;
      margin-top: 2px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .used-by {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      color: #6a6a73;
      margin: 8px 0 10px;
    }
    .used-by code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
      background: rgba(127,127,140,0.12);
      padding: 1px 4px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    pre {
      background: #f4f4f6;
      border: 1px solid #e3e3e8;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px;
      overflow: auto;
      font-size: 11.5px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      max-height: 60vh;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }
    a { color: #0a6cff; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Drittanbieter-Lizenzen</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    <strong>budget-app</strong> ist lizenziert unter
    <strong>GPL-3.0-or-later</strong> (siehe <code>COPYING</code> im Source-Repository).
    Dieser Bericht listet alle Rust-Abhängigkeiten der nativen Binary und ihre Lizenzen
    nach SPDX-ID, gefolgt vom jeweiligen Lizenztext.
    Eine entsprechende Liste für JavaScript-Pakete erzeugt
    <code>pnpm licenses:js</code>.
  </p>

  <h2>Übersicht</h2>
  <div class="summary-card">
    <ul>
      {{#each overview}}
        <li><strong>{{name}}</strong> <span class="pill">{{count}}</span></li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </div>

  {{#each licenses}}
    <h2>{{name}} <span class="pill">{{id}}</span></h2>
    {{#each used_by}}
      <details>
        <summary>
          {{crate.name}}
          <span class="meta">
            v{{crate.version}}{{#if crate.repository}} ·
              <a href="{{crate.repository}}">{{crate.repository}}</a>
            {{/if}}
          </span>
        </summary>
      </details>
    {{/each}}
    <details>
      <summary>Volltext der Lizenz</summary>
      <pre>{{text}}</pre>
    </details>
  {{/each}}

  <h2>Hinweis</h2>
  <p class="meta">
    Dieser Bericht wird automatisch von
    <a href="https://github.com/EmbarkStudios/cargo-about">cargo-about</a>
    erzeugt und sollte bei jedem Release aktualisiert werden
    (<code>pnpm licenses</code>).
  </p>
</body>
</html>
